OL,3,CMum of teenager who died in crash
OL,4,Ccondemns scheme that can release
OL,5,Cdriver early
OL,7,FThe mother of a teenager who died in a
OL,8,Fcar crash has hit out at a scheme
OL,9,Fwhich could see the driver released
OL,10,Fearly from prison.
OL,12,FChloe Hayman was just 17 when she died
OL,13,Fin July 2022, killed in a car crash
OL,14,Fnear Fochriw in Caerphilly county.
OL,16,FKeilan Roberts, who was at the wheel,
OL,17,Fwas over the limit for alcohol and had
OL,18,Falso taken cocaine, ecstasy and
OL,19,Fketamine.
