OL,3,CMum of teenager who died in crash
OL,4,Ccondemns scheme that can release
OL,5,Cdriver early
OL,7,FThe pair had only met that evening at
OL,8,Fa nightclub in Pontypridd, and Roberts
OL,9,Fdrove despite the pleas of friends not
OL,10,Fto take the wheel.
OL,12,FLast year, he was sentenced to 5 years
OL,13,Fand 3 months for causing death by
OL,14,Fcareless driving.
OL,16,FBut he could be out as soon as next
OL,17,Fspring, following UK government
OL,18,Fchanges to sentencing rules.
OL,20,FChloe's mother, Danielle O'Halloran,
OL,21,Fsays that is wrong.
