OL,3,CMum of teenager who died in crash
OL,4,Ccondemns scheme that can release
OL,5,Cdriver early
OL,7,F"He's only been in prison a year and
OL,8,Fhe's already been moved to an open
OL,9,Fprison," she told ITV Cymru Wales.
OL,11,FShe added: "And with this new scheme,
OL,12,Fit's just too much - we're not going
OL,13,Fto see Chloe ever again. He's going to
OL,14,Fhave the rest of his life to come out
OL,15,Fand rebuild his life"
OL,17,F"I don't think this should be given to
OL,18,Fpeople."
