OL,4,Ccondemns scheme that can release
OL,5,Cdriver early
OL,7,FThe new Lord Chancellor and Justice
OL,8,FSecretary, Shabana Mahmoud, announced
OL,9,Frecently that current rules about
OL,10,Fprisoner release - known as the "End
OL,11,Fof Custody Supervised Licence" - would
OL,12,Fbe relaxed.
OL,14,FIt means offenders serving time for
OL,15,Fless serious crimes could be let out
OL,16,Fafter 40 per cent of their sentence,
OL,17,Frather than the current 50 per cent.
