OL,7,FThe move is intended to free up space,
OL,8,Fwith prisons in England and Wales
OL,9,Fhaving been at more than 99% capacity
OL,10,Fevery month bar one this year.
OL,12,FPrison reformers say the move is
OL,13,Fdesperately needed to prevent prison
OL,14,Fviolence and stop further offending on
OL,15,Fthe outside.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/10
