OL,3,CMum of teenager who died in crash
OL,4,Ccondemns scheme that can release
OL,5,Cdriver early
OL,7,F"There is not enough space in the
OL,8,Fsystem to give (prisoners) the
OL,9,Fcourses, the education, the
OL,10,Fintervention that they need in order
OL,11,Fto turn their lives around and turn
OL,12,Faway from offending," said Andrea
OL,13,FCoomber KC, from the Howard League for
OL,14,FPenal Reform.
OL,16,FAndrea said: "It's the only way,
OL,17,Ffrankly, to buy the government some
OL,18,Fheadroom to decide what they want to
OL,19,Fdo with the prison system, because our
OL,20,Fprisons are simply awful."
