OL,3,CMum of teenager who died in crash
OL,4,Ccondemns scheme that can release
OL,5,Cdriver early
OL,7,F"Ever longer sentences mean (inmates)
OL,8,Faren't being released in the way they
OL,9,Fused to be,"
OL,11,F"And that means you can't use prison
OL,12,Ffor people who are dangerous and
OL,13,Freally need to be in prison."
OL,15,FSentences for serious violent offences
OL,16,Fof four years or more, as well as sex
OL,17,Foffences, will be automatically
OL,18,Fexcluded from the new scheme.
