OL,4,Ccondemns scheme that can release
OL,5,Cdriver early
OL,7,FWhile the early release of offenders
OL,8,Fin prison for domestic abuse connected
OL,9,Fcrimes - such as stalking and
OL,10,Fcontrolling or coercive behaviour -
OL,11,Fwill also be disallowed.
OL,13,FA spokesperson for the Ministry of
OL,14,FJustice said the prison system was "in
OL,15,Fcrisis."
OL,17,F"If we fail to act now, we face a
OL,18,Ftotal breakdown of law and order,
OL,19,Fputting victims at greater risk", the
OL,20,Fstatement said.
