OL,4,Ccondemns scheme that can release
OL,5,Cdriver early
OL,7,F"We are working with partners to
OL,8,Fmanage the impact of these changes,
OL,9,Fincluding on victims"
OL,11,F"The Lord Chancellor has also
OL,12,Fcommitted to recruiting 1,000 trainee
OL,13,Fprobation officers to strengthen
OL,14,Fsupervision in the community and
OL,15,Fbetter protect the public."
OL,17,FBack in Wales, Danielle says she's
OL,18,Fdetermined to remain as positive as
OL,19,Fpossible for her two remaining
OL,20,Fchildren.
