OL,3,CMum of teenager who died in crash
OL,4,Ccondemns scheme that can release
OL,5,Cdriver early
OL,7,FShe said: "I don't want to be a
OL,8,Fmiserable, depressed mother. I just
OL,9,Fwant to be as happy as I can be for
OL,10,Fthem.
OL,12,F"I want to be a role model for them
OL,13,Fthat whatever happens in life we don't
OL,14,Fhave to go down that rabbit hole. We
OL,15,Fdon't have to sit in sadness and go
OL,16,Fdown that dark hole."
OL,18,FIn the ongoing debate over whether
OL,19,Fprison is working, she's also
OL,20,Fdetermined that the voice of the
OL,21,Fvictim continues to shine through.
